            <p>
                This is a device that converts DC electricity into AC electricity, allowing the PV system to be used for appliances that require AC current. Inverters come in various forms and designs,
                There are 3 basic types of inverters which are Square wave, Modified (quasi) square wave and Sine wave.
            </p>
